                      <additions>
                        <list>
                          <item xml:id="a1">
                            <locus target="#5r"/>
                            <desc type="DonationNote">The donation note states that the book was entrusted to <persName ref="PRS4805Grebaut" role="owner"/> to be sent to the papal
                              library in Rome. The note also mentions the donor, <persName ref="PRS4300GabraMa" role="donor"><roleName type="title">ʾAbbā</roleName> 
                                Gabra Madḫǝn Ǧǝrom Gabra Muse</persName>. The note was written in <placeName ref="LOC1216AddisA">ʾAddis ʾAbabā</placeName> on 
                              <date>28 Yakkātit 1918</date>, i.e. in <date when="1926"/>.</desc>
                            <q xml:lang="gez">ተፈነወት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በእዴ<lb/>ሁ፡ ለአብ፡ ኅሩይ፡ አባ፡ <persName ref="PRS4805Grebaut" role="owner">ግሬቦ፡
                              ሲል<lb/>ቤን።</persName> ለትብጻሕ፡ ኀበ፡ ብሔረ፡ ሮ<lb/>ሜ፡ ውስተ፡ መዛግብተ፡ መጻሕፍ<lb/>ቲሆሙ፡ ለሊቀ፡ ጳጳስ። ይቤ፡ 
                              ጸጋዊሃ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> <lb/> ለዛቲ፡ <persName ref="PRS4300GabraMa" role="donor"><roleName type="title">አባ፡</roleName>
                                ገብረ፡ መድኅን፡ ጀሮም፡ ገ<lb/>ብረ፡ ሙሴ።</persName> ሐዲስ፡ አበባ። <lb/> ፳፰የካቲት፡ ፲፱፻፲፰።</q>
                          </item>
                          
                          <item xml:id="a2">                          
                            <locus target="#6v"/>
                            <desc type="Record">The note certifies that <persName ref="PRS15084Bezunah">Lǝǧ Bǝzunah</persName> gave 
                              <persName ref="PRS15085Taddasa">Tāddasa</persName> a revolver after being appointed <foreign xml:lang="am">getā</foreign>. 
                              The note was written in 1911 year of mercy, i.e. <date when="1919"/>.</desc>
                            <q xml:lang="am">
                              ፲፱፻፲፩ዓመተ፡ ምህረት<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ተጻፈ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> <lb/> ልጅ፡ ብዙነህ፡ <sic>ለከርሞ፡</sic>
                              <lb/> ጌታ፡ ሊሆን፡ ፩፡ <choice><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ሽጉጥ፡</corr><sic>ሸጉጥ፡</sic></choice> 
                              <del rend="effaced">እ</del><lb/>ለታደሰ፡ <choice><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">እሸልምኃለሁ፡</corr><sic>እሸልመኃለሁ፡</sic></choice> <lb/>
                              ብሎ፡ ውል፡ ወረቀት፡ ነው፡ <lb/> ቃል፡ ነውና፡ <choice><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">አይጠፋም</corr><sic>አይ<del rend="effaced">ጣ</del>ጠፍም</sic></choice><supplied reason="omitted">።</supplied>
                            </q>
                          </item>
                          
